paragraph: Picky Talarico is a film director and photographer who has directed music videos for artists like Juanes, Julieta Venegas, Paulina Rubio, Diego Torres, Julio Iglesias, Gustavo Cerati, Kevin Johansen, and Bajofondo.
He has been nominated for two Latin Grammy Awards and five MTV Video Music Awards among other multiple awards around the globe.
